                <li><p><strong>THE NORTH FACE</strong><br>Named after the coldest part of a mountain, The North Face has been providing extreme sports enthusiasts and explorers with performance outerwear and accessories for over 50 years. Whether you&rsquo;re into skiing, snowboarding or hiking, The North Face has the perfect jackets, fleeces, pants, hats and gloves for your adventures. Featuring cutting-edge PrimaLoft<sup>&reg;</sup> ThermoBall<sup>&trade;</sup> insulation and breathable technologies, The North Face&rsquo;s outerwear collection is a winner to keep you warm and dry during all your winter activities. Find the latest gear from The North Face at Macy&rsquo;s!</p></li>
